Daniel Cardenas 
.description
Experts Only Mercenary Simulator.  A neat (and tough!) PD game that was
originally developed for eventual commercial release but for various
reasons the author decided to release as PD instead.  So far my son has
beat every other Amiga game I've got, both PD and commercial, but he gave
up on this one.  For serious game players.  
